# Real Images Folder

Place real (genuine, unmanipulated) face images in this folder.

## Labeling

All images in this folder will automatically be labeled as:
- **Class: Real**
- **Label: 0**

## Tips

- Use clear, well-lit photographs
- Include diverse faces (different ages, ethnicities, genders)
- Various angles and expressions help model generalization
- Avoid heavily filtered or edited (but not deepfake) images
